Dan Anderson sraral hya'ga sisyow na NBA, wal malaxmisoq qaniy la. kawas te 1951, byacing te 1 ro 1 ryax qo hintgan nya, kinholan nya ga California, hiya ga mnanak na ppzoy mari waya, ro sqoliq ka ppkal mari waya. 188 konbon kinwagiq nya, 84 konkin kin'sow nya, hiya ga qotox nqo spzyang blaq na ppzoy mari NBA. kawas 1974 mnwayaw ppzoy mari ga, mzyop sqo te qotox lahoy ro te magal sqoliq, galon nqo Portland Trail Blazers. qnxan nya Dan Anderson NBA wal wayan mhngaw lga,成為 tmngasal na sqoilq ro mtzyaw qhoniq na sqoilq.qotox qotox kawas tmngasal qotox pgal 間. cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro' Lists of National Basketball Association players
